01:39:06.840 --> 01:39:08.140
in the [inaudible].

01:39:08.140 --> 01:39:09.760
I mean, it's too close
to rock and roll, right?

01:39:09.760 --> 01:39:12.110
&gt;&gt; Larry Applebaum:
Lot of nice stories.

